
ping:
======
ping command or service is used for test the route status.
	sync : ping -c 4 remotemachineip

		or
		ping remotemachineipaddress
		
*****imp which service is used for ping?

	-->it use the ICMP protocol 	
    -->ICMP means (internet control message protocol) in the network it use port number also
	
*****imp what is the port number of ICMP?
		7